        MD Utilities
        ============
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/cmayes/md_utils.svg
                :target: https://travis-ci.org/cmayes/md_utils
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/md_utils.svg
